{"title_page": "Alejandro Rojas", "text_new": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Alejandro Rojas\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Chilean\n| sport          = [[rowing (sport)|Rowing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1962|1|6|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Alejandro Rojas''' (born 6 January 1962) is a Chilean [[rowing (sport)|rower]]. He competed at the [[1984 Summer Olympics]] and the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ro/alejandro-rojas-1.html |title=Alejandro Rojas Olympic Results |accessdate=4 September 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Rojas, Alejandro}}\n[[Category:1962 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:Chilean male rowers]]\n[[Category:Olympic rowers of Chile]]\n[[Category:Rowers at the 1984 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Rowers at the 1988 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Place of birth missing (living people)]]\n[[Category:Pan American Games medalists in rowing]]\n\n\n{{Chile-rowing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2018}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Alejandro Rojas\n| full_name      = \n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| nationality    = Chilean\n| sport          = [[rowing (sport)|Rowing]]\n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1962|1|6|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n}}\n\n'''Alejandro Rojas''' (born 6 January 1962) is a Chilean [[rowing (sport)|rower]]. He competed at the [[1984 Summer Olympics]] and the [[1988 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"SportsRef\">{{cite Sports-Reference |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/ro/alejandro-rojas-1.html |title=Alejandro Rojas Olympic Results |accessdate=4 September 2018}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{re